schema.name: store_number
schema.description: Unique number assigned to the store who ordered the liquor.

schema.name: store_name
schema.description: Name of store who ordered the liquor.

schema.name: address
schema.description: Address of store who ordered the liquor.

schema.name: city
schema.description: City where the store who ordered the liquor is located

schema.name: zip_code
schema.description: Zip code where the store who ordered the liquor is located

schema.name: store_location
schema.description: Location of store who ordered the liquor. The Address, City, State and Zip Code are geocoded to provide geographic coordinates. Accuracy of geocoding is dependent on how well the address is interpreted and the completeness of the reference data used.

schema.name: county_number
schema.description: Iowa county number for the county where store who ordered the liquor is located

schema.name: county
schema.description: County where the store who ordered the liquor is located
